{"tid":1351852,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"已經開始有fd唔敢著黑衫出街，要著白衫........","createTime":"2019-07-22T16:36:01.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-22T18:37:13.000Z","uid":58335,"like":66,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"54257fcb250c030f2ba86525ca1fb4f5e839b33f","tid":1351852,"uid":58335,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-22T16:36:01.000Z","msg":"黑社會傳聞開大片<br />\n黑警竟然一句野都冇講過<br />\n成個元朗好似死成咁<br />\n我真係冇諗過2019年竟然會見到呢D野<br />\n我以為佢地起碼都交下戲<br />\n點知戲都懶得交<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n有個fd唔係住新界<br />\n但佢話返工唔敢著黑衫出街，要著白衫<br />\n有人打人應該唔會打佢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n係大學又聽到有人話唔著黑衫<br />\n你睇下個社會變成點<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">不過我就唔會唔著黑衫出街<br />\n我唔著黑衫，即係向惡勢力低頭<br />\n我就日日著<br />\n睇下你班仆街係咪大撚曬<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span></span>"},{"pid":"3d28eaf8efb5ecfa581ddb6b61b34f7a99c384f3","tid":1351852,"uid":224763,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-22T16:39:59.000Z","msg":"Agger"},{"pid":"8d245c8686a4773956a2c89a57377359e042ac4d","tid":1351852,"uid":58335,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-22T16:50:07.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d56fa98a1c4a202ca58bc9e12b61a35e8e1b9e9a","tid":1351852,"uid":106929,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-22T16:53:02.000Z","msg":"香港人唔可以向惡勢力屈服<br />\n<br />\n星期三睇波著黑衫支持"},{"pid":"4995198e4a8a1a427653e082eb9697f0503b9521","tid":1351852,"uid":58335,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"d56fa98a1c4a202ca58bc9e12b61a35e8e1b9e9a","tid":1351852,"uid":106929,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-22T16:53:02.000Z","msg":"香港人唔可以向惡勢力屈服<br />\n<br />\n星期三睇波